# Setup Let encrypt SSL for iRedMail

Tài liệu tham khảo: https://azdigi.com/blog/huong-dan/email-server/cai-dat-lets-encrypt-ssl-cho-iredmail/

## Step 1: Update and setup certbot for nginx
```
sudo apt update
sudo apt install certbot
```
## Step 2: Setup SSL Let's EnCrypt
```
certbot certonly --webroot -w /var/www/html -d mail.nexlesoft.io.vn
```
## Step 3: Set config let's encrypt iRedMail
Remove 2 file old key ssl for iRedMail
```
rm -f /etc/ssl/private/iRedMail.key
rm -f /etc/ssl/certs/iRedMail.crt
```
and set symbol links
```
ln -s /etc/letsencrypt/live/mail.nexlesoft.io.vn/privkey.pem /etc/ssl/private/iRedMail.key
ln -s /etc/letsencrypt/live/mail.nexlesoft.io.vn/fullchain.pem /etc/ssl/certs/iRedMail.crt
```
